  "original_lang": "si",
  "original_title": "\u2019\u2019\u0dbb\u0da7\u0dda \u0db4\u0dcf\u0dbd\u0db1\u0dba \u0db6\u0dcf\u0dbb\u0d9c\u0db1\u0dca\u0db1 \u0dc3\u0dd6\u0daf\u0dcf\u0db1\u0db8\u0dca\u2019\u2019",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "\"Ready to take control of the country\"",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Janatha Vimukthi Peramuna leader and Member of Parliament Mr. Anura Kumara Dissanayake said today that he is ready to take over if the government of the country is handed over at this time.",
        "Anura Kumara Mahata also mentioned that 'we are people who are ready to accept the responsibility and do not leave anything out of fear.'",
        "But since there are only three representatives in the parliament, if the bills of the president and the prime minister are there in the parliament, there is a chance for someone else to become the president and prime minister.",
        "Mr. Dissanayake also said that since a contradiction has been created between the will of the people and the parliament, a parliament that reflects the will of the people should be established."
      ],
